data.description: The Evergreen ranch-style floor plan features 2 beds/2.5 baths, an office w/french doors, 3.5-car garage, full unfinished basement and back open space! Home has a spacious kitchen with gray painted cabinets & island. Great room has a 2-way fireplace that looks out to a covered patio. The master has a luxury 5 piece bathroom w/spacious closet that is connected to the laundry room. This home is Energy Star 3.0 Certified.
